        <div class="body">
            <p>The render method of Zend_Form_Element_Captcha calls the generate method of Zend_Captcha_Adapter.  Therefore when rendering each element of a Captcha in a ViewScript, the Captcha image/word is generated for each element.</p>

<p>In the example above each time the form is rendered 3 seperate Captcha images will be generated.</p>

